Create a playbook content.yml and it should run on dev group.
i) Create a directory /web and it should be owned by ansi_user group.
ii) /web directory should have context type as "httpd"
iii) Assign the permission for user=rwx,group=rwx,others=rx and group special permission
should be applied to /web.
iv) Create an index.html file under /web directory and the file should have the content
"Learning Ansible".
v) Link the /web directory to /var/www/html/web.
